We are delighted to invite you to the celebration of our marriage

Thompson William

William, a graduate from the realm of knowledge, Embarking on a new chapter, a journey to acknowledge. With a heart entwined in code, a software sage, He finds solace in fishing and camping's rustic stage. In the realm of technology, he shines ever bright, Yet seeks the tranquility of nature's calming light. Now as he prepares to say "I do," with love's flare, May his marriage be as serene as a peaceful river's lair.

Isabella Rodriguez

Issabella, a graduate of wisdom's embrace, Embarking on a journey with elegance and grace. In the world of software, she finds her stride, While diving into books and swimming's rhythmic tide. Her mind a canvas, where stories come alive, Imagination's realm, where she'll forever thrive. As she joins hands with love's eternal flame, May her marriage be a tale of bliss, never tame.
